data.description: Looking for new construction without the wait? This lovely, spacious full brick home was built in 2020! Owners are relocating for work and hate to leave their dream home. However, you can now make it your family dream home instead. Features split bedroom floor plan with two full baths. Trey ceiling in master bedroom and family room. Two car garage with remotes. Alarm system will remain with home. Home built in cul-de-sac. Community has large in-ground pool 11 acre lake. Shopping and restaurants minutes away.
